  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "tutorial-backup-restore-01",
      "markerIndex": 0,
      "replayStartSec": 2.409089,
      "replayEndSec": 6.555802,
      "narrationText": "第一步。让我们导入现有的 rclone 配置。rclone 支持 S3、Backblaze、Google Drive、Dropbox 等众多服务，如果你已经在使用，可以直接导入同一份配置。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-01.a20da912.mp3",
      "textHash": "a20da912d12ad42d9ec57c6c136b3ab197fd4e53aad643d7f18cec06d39cb61c",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.00898,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-01-after.0d8e1904.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.989388,
      "afterTextHash": "0d8e19042b1813318fe980b48e68056df67b41a75c610450f6ed7736e48c2c18"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-backup-restore-02",
      "markerIndex": 1,
      "replayStartSec": 6.555802,
      "replayEndSec": 10.251839,
      "narrationText": "让我们列出命令行工具现在已知的存储。每个存储都是我们可以推送备份的目标。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-02.af2bf87c.mp3",
      "textHash": "af2bf87c7956eaf2971615ffd5b909dc38761285824e2807c725bd6689480ba1",
      "audioDurationSec": 6.347755,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-02-after.ae9ace8b.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.970612,
      "afterTextHash": "ae9ace8b950ed304afa4de8f943bc3abcf227ffba64093fb1e65cc9cf23bf2c6"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-backup-restore-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 10.251839,
      "replayEndSec": 24.484571,
      "narrationText": "第二步。让我们推送一个完整备份。整个仓库，包括应用、数据库、文件和配置，全部上传。由于仓库本身是静态加密的，备份也是加密的，无需额外的密钥管理。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-03.70dbeca1.mp3",
      "textHash": "70dbeca190def8f2e7c987c49c3adeed82131ab0e47aebc516869f465644955e",
      "audioDurationSec": 16.666122,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-03-after.a250b728.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 5.32898,
      "afterTextHash": "a250b7282a14747f0d1b6adfc12c29d5ceca746b5dfa1cfcdd3ff801efcc5db0"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-backup-restore-04",
      "markerIndex": 3,
      "replayStartSec": 24.484571,
      "replayEndSec": 31.133919,
      "narrationText": "让我们列出该存储上的可用备份。从这里开始，在全新服务器上恢复只需一条命令，即仓库拉取命令。相同的数据，相同的容器，不同的机器。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-04.c62a3ed7.mp3",
      "textHash": "c62a3ed770b84d6b5ee55a11245cb55f0d5e4f9bdb23edc96af1cdb16777fb94",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.635918,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-04-after.c0575810.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.362449,
      "afterTextHash": "c05758109ce281877a9ede44696ac65597742b0d33acad73c35a802288488290"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-backup-restore-05",
      "markerIndex": 4,
      "replayStartSec": 31.133919,
      "replayEndSec": 39.135694,
      "narrationText": "现在来验证恢复过程。首先将 repository 下线：停止服务并卸载加密卷。这台机器上的应用已经消失了。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-05.77930f35.mp3",
      "textHash": "77930f356d9e2f0b4cf37d5e83b9d8d44375cdcab9d7dc83c89fc3802e8510f6",
      "audioDurationSec": 8.437551,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-05-after.e59c8f9f.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.519184,
      "afterTextHash": "e59c8f9fcc0014124639f425f676a9d34727d1e5695c3223629f84d58eb03d92"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-backup-restore-06",
      "markerIndex": 5,
      "replayStartSec": 39.135694,
      "replayEndSec": 48.126162,
      "narrationText": "然后直接从存储中拉取备份。repo pull 命令会获取镜像、检查完整性，并将其放回原位。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-06.af021282.mp3",
      "textHash": "af021282eae59b981bad65ac637f8ce4cf254bf4974550c56e3ea877d7f82344",
      "audioDurationSec": 9.090612,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-06-after.ee397f29.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.597551,
      "afterTextHash": "ee397f29ab2dac58bf6c833829b50808a02f9847c20cb447a4138682610205e0"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-backup-restore-07",
      "markerIndex": 6,
      "replayStartSec": 48.126162,
      "replayEndSec": 54.070366,
      "narrationText": "再次挂载，repository 就恢复了。Push、list、pull，这就是备份的完整流程。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-07.68d3e074.mp3",
      "textHash": "68d3e074d7e5e6497873ab2987ac6b1b934fa6b5ea099d82a17d9eae07c525a7",
      "audioDurationSec": 6.687347,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/tutorial-backup-restore-07-after.b3d27e96.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.63102,
      "afterTextHash": "b3d27e96a6b8c10c041dda8dfce1ee4a46bc4ebe60cde015145f044d6aa4679a"
    }
  ],
  "narrationAudio": [
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "textHash": "5448584af3d47f7cbe3f1d9fb9a5e12c20ce7cf22a3c3f0cfc40e6039b763d5c",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/intro.5448584a.mp3",
      "narrationText": "你的应用已经上线，那就来确保它绝不会丢失！在本教程中，我们会把整个仓库推送到外部存储，并按需拉回来。",
      "audioDurationSec": 10.605714
    },
    {
      "id": "three-steps",
      "textHash": "7c3dd6d386f2df9b6f398b357d36c46915686e0265b78a3dab1a76b19c537687",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-backup-restore/three-steps.7c3dd6d3.mp3",
      "narrationText": "备份与恢复归结为三个步骤：配置存储提供商、推送备份，以及在需要时恢复它。",
      "audioDurationSec": 9.247347
    },
